body:
So Riot has managed to ruin one of the best game modes in the game by catering to people who can&#039;t seem to be able to have fun playing what they want against other people who play what they want. They seem to be enjoying it more when you&#039;re forced to play something even if it&#039;s horrible and getting waffle stomped by that one random good champ. So I propose a solution, or a compromise if you will. Both game modes are released under the Urf tab. That way people who have fun playing what they want against people who also play what they want can play Classic Urf. People who have fun seeing different champions but for some reason don&#039;t want to play ARAM can play ARURF.

This way people can play what they want.
